{"id":396023,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/微在-10-个让你觉得群众很愚蠢的时刻/","date":"2015-06-22T07:05:04Z","modified":"2017-12-25T10:54:18Z","title":"微在 | 10 个让你觉得群众很愚蠢的时刻","content":"<p>古斯塔夫·勒庞在《乌合之众》中说道：“人一到群体中，智商就严重降低，为了获得认同，个体愿意抛弃是非，用智商去换取那份让人备感安全的归属感。”生活中，你是否有过群众很愚蠢的想法？以下是 10 个具有代表性的群众愚蠢时刻：</p>\n<p>1. “崔永元：‘你学过播音主持吗？你有什么资格和我争论？’下面一群人叫好时。” @赵力</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/崔永元.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396024\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/崔永元.jpg\" alt=\"崔永元\" width=\"600\" height=\"212\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/崔永元.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/崔永元-300x106.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. “ 360 发布安全路由器有人为了其孕妇模式交智商税时。” @赵力</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/360.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396025\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/360.jpg\" alt=\"360\" width=\"596\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/360.jpg 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/360-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 596px) 100vw, 596px\" /></a></p>\n<p>3. “有时看网易、腾讯新闻下方评论的时候。” @Gary Wang</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/新闻评论.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396026\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/新闻评论.jpg\" alt=\"新闻评论\" width=\"601\" height=\"669\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/新闻评论.jpg 601w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/新闻评论-270x300.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 601px) 100vw, 601px\" /></a></p>\n<p>4. “非典抢购板蓝根，白醋，福岛事件时抢盐。” @胡静</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/抢盐.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396028\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/抢盐.jpg\" alt=\"抢盐\" width=\"599\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/抢盐.jpg 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/抢盐-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></a></p>\n<p>5. “《小时代》《战狼》这些垃圾票房几亿。” @胡静</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾票房.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396027\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾票房.jpg\" alt=\"垃圾票房\" width=\"600\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾票房.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾票房-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>6. “坐月子不洗澡不下床喝米酒。” @胡静</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/坐月子.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396030\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/坐月子.jpg\" alt=\"坐月子\" width=\"600\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/坐月子.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/坐月子-300x228.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>7. “灾难时在网上比哪个明星捐款多，捐的少就骂。” @胡静</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/灾难捐款.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396029\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/灾难捐款.jpg\" alt=\"灾难捐款\" width=\"598\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/灾难捐款.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/灾难捐款-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a></p>\n<p>8. “打开各大电商选购图书频道，看到各畅销榜上面推荐列表上面九成都是垃圾书的时候。” @胡静</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾书.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396033\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾书.jpg\" alt=\"垃圾书\" width=\"598\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾书.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/垃圾书-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a></p>\n<p>9. “前脚骂棒子，后脚喊偶吧。” @JYEllen</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/哈韩.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396031\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/哈韩.jpg\" alt=\"哈韩\" width=\"600\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/哈韩.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/哈韩-300x232.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>10. “湖南卫视的收视率。” @不二</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/湖南卫视.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396032\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/湖南卫视.jpg\" alt=\"湖南卫视\" width=\"599\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/湖南卫视.jpg 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/湖南卫视-300x197.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/湖南卫视-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[28021,33704,33153,9918,21139,15083]}